metadata.name: The White Lily Witch
metadata.description:
Once upon a time, amber was a very precious mineral, and the only way to make it was through forbidden alchemy.

"Deep in the forest, beyond a field of white lilies, there is a secluded mansion where a witch lives. And she was the only one who knew how to make amber from honey."
A young man heard this rumor and came all the way to ask her to produce amber. Because he desperately needed it for a certain revenge.

She said to him, "Are you prepared to sacrifice half of your life?”
